<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="narrowly-adv">narrowly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'nærəʊli/    美 /'næroʊli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>勉强地；差点儿 (没)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The car narrowly missed a cyclist. 
汽车差点儿撞上一位骑自行车的人。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The final score of the basketball match was 93-94. We were only  <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (narrow) beaten.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. narrowly  </p></div>